title: Happy National Pass Gas Day
itunes:title: Happy National Pass Gas Day
description:
The Breakfast Club is back with all the members, and to start it off we opened up the phone lines to see what our listeners thought about George Lopez jokingly responding about collecting a rumored bounty on Donald Trump. Also since it is National pass gas day we opened up the phone lines for listeners to share their gas stories and Donald Trump gave "Donkey of the Day" to a Michigan man who cannibalized and killed someone.
